    Hoist loop-invariant math out of filter hot loops (#696)

    * Hoist loop-invariant math out of filter hot loops

    - ColorHalftoneFilter: precompute sin/cos of the three screen angles
      once before the row loop instead of recomputing them for every
      row x channel (2 * height * 3 trig calls reduced to 6).
