    Validate ColorHalftoneFilter and CrystallizeFilter sizing parameters (#494)

    ColorHalftoneFilter: jhlabs computes `gridSize = 2 * radius * √2` and
    then `ImageMath.mod(tx, gridSize)`. radius == 0 produces gridSize ==
    0 and divides by zero, propagating NaN through the whole image.

