    The constructor parameter on both Arc and FilledArc was called
    "endAngle", which strongly suggests an absolute angle "draw from
    startAngle to endAngle". But it was passed unmodified to
    Graphics2D.drawArc / fillArc, which take an arcAngle (the angular
    span starting at startAngle), not an absolute end.

